Ethics: Will you receive the data already anonymized or will you do the anonymization? If you use any data that is still identifiable including pseudonymous data please register this via a PRET application, for more information: https://admin.kuleuven.be/privacy/studpers/index
Sharing: Please note that Zenodo is a repository, not a preprint server, the data sharing section concerns the data, including code, underlying publications, not the publications themselves. KU Leuven also has its own repository that you can use for data preservation and sharing: https://www.kuleuven.be/rdm/en/rdr, both Zenodo and RDR will add a DOI to the data upon deposit
